author: Rick Cantu
title: Vandegrift storms back to defeat Vista Ridge 63-55
text:
Vandegrift’s football players were staring atthe wrong end of a 42-14 score Friday night as Travis Brannan grewincreasingly agitated on the home sideline at Monroe Stadium.
“More than anything, I wanted the ball!” said Brannan, a senior running back for the state-ranked Vipers. “I was begging for the football.”
